	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64427290">Most office PC's used in business aren't going to be used for AI. They're for users running in house software, word processing, web browsing, accounting and other mundane business tasks. How is AI going to increase a worker's productivity typing out a memo?

<br> <br>
For home users, using AI for little Johnny's term paper will just get him an F.
<br> <br>
MS needs to release a non-AI version for just plain workloads.</div>
